skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: super hero facts
des:
This skill will tell you very interesting facts about the Marvel and DC in general, as well as facts about your favorite characters.
The characters include :
 Spider Man,
 Captain Marvel, 
 Hulk,
 Thor,
 Iron Man,
 Captain America,
 Black Widow,
 Black Panther,
 Falcon,
 Scarlet Witch,
 Vision,
 Ant Man,
 Doctor Strange,
 Loki,
 Venom,
 Deadpool and
 Thanos
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
